response.job_title: Senior Bid officer at Siemens Mobility
response.summary: Electrical Engineering Master's graduate specializing in Power Systems and Rail Infrastructure. Committed to continuous growth and achieving goals. Experienced in agile project management for efficient execution. Fluent in English, German, and Spanish (native speaker) with strong interpersonal skills and cultural awareness. Ready to contribute to international teams.
response.skills: Bid Writing, Stakeholder Management, Computer-Aided Design (CAD), Sales, Negotiation, Interkulturelle Kompetenzen, Railway Electrification Systems

profile_positions.description:
In my current role I create Rail Infrastructure offers for the German market for both people and goods
transportation according to specified calculation guidelines. I ensure the usability of the requested
materials by carrying out technical clarifications. Moreover, I develop customer strategies and involve
our cross-functional interface partners such as Purchasing or Engineering whenever relevant.
Additionally, as iTWO Administrator I make sure that the platform is up and running and compliant with
internal security standards at all times.
